<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1799944-what-age-is-appropriate-for-this-book-my">What age is appropriate for this book? My eight year is an advanced reader who reads everything she gets her hands on, she just finished and loved the 
Laura Ingalls Wilder series and so my husband thought she might enjoy this but I fear it&#39;s a bit heavy and dark for her yet.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1799944'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F257845.True_Grit">like</a></span>

